===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|transport||}}

#To [[change]] the [[location]] or [[place]] of.
#To [[deport]] to a [[penal]] [[colony]].
#To [[move]] (someone) to [[strong]] [[emotion]]; to [[carry away]].

